videos.headline: Auburn's Johnson shakes off defenders for TD
videos.description: Kerryon Johnson rushes up the middle for an 8-yard touchdown, his 17th on the season.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe's Gore breaks out for long gain
videos.description: Caleb Evans completes a pass on the outside to Derrick Gore for a 36-yard gain in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe executes double reverse for TD
videos.description: Derrick Gore takes the toss and hands the ball off to Brian Williams for a 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Warhawks force 1st INT
videos.description: Auburn's Jarrett Stidham tries forcing a pass to  Eli Stove but is picked off by Ronald Jenkins in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe's Green reels in great catch
videos.description: Caleb Evans lofts a pass to Marcus Green who lays out and makes the spectacular catch for a 10-yard gain.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe's Turner hauls in tipped pass
videos.description: Caleb Evans' pass attempt is tipped by Auburn DB Carlton Davis but is still hauled in by RJ Turner in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Auburn forces big 3rd down stop
videos.description: Caleb Evans is under heavy pressure and is sacked by Deshaun Davis to force 4th down.

videos.headline: Auburn's Stidham connects with Slayton for long TD
videos.description: Jarrett Stidham throws a pass down the sideline to Darius Slayton for a 50-yard touchdown late in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Malzahn: 'We didn't play very good in the first half'
videos.description: Gus Malzahn acknowledges Auburn's slow start in the first half and says the team needs to show more urgency in the second half.

videos.headline: Auburn's Martin breaks free for long run
videos.description: Kam Martin rushes up the middle and gains 31-yards to put the Tigers in the red zone.

videos.headline: Auburn's Martin caps drive off with TD
videos.description: Following a long 31-yard rush, Kam Martin finishes the drive rushing up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Auburn forces Smith INT
videos.description: Backup QB Garrett Smith tries forcing a pass to Brian Williams in tight coverage but is picked off by Auburn DB Javaris Davis.

videos.headline: Auburn's Stidham links up with Martin for TD
videos.description: Jarrett Stidham throws his second touchdown of the day, this time to Kam Martin for a 41-yard score.

videos.headline: Auburn's Davis forces fumble
videos.description: Garrett Smith completes a pass over the middle to Brian Williams, but after gaining 11 yards, Javaris Davis strips the ball for Auburn's second forced turnover.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe forces 2nd turnover
videos.description: Jarrett Stidham mishandles the snap and loses the ball in the red zone for a turnover in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Ruffin extends Auburn lead on pick-six
videos.description: Garrett Smith tries forcing a pass to D'Marius Gillespie but it's picked off by Nick Ruffin, who goes all the way for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe's Smith finds Williams for long TD
videos.description: Garrett Smith completes a pass to Brian Williams on the outside for a 70-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Auburn's Willis finds opening for long run
videos.description: Malik Willis takes the handoff to the outside and rushes for 62 yards to put the Tigers back in the red zone.

videos.headline: Malzahn: 'I'm proud of our team'
videos.description: After a slow start in the first half, Gus Malzahn and the Tigers came out with "championship urgency" in the second half to beat Louisiana Monroe 42-14.

videos.headline: Auburn cruises to 9th win
videos.description: Kerryon Johnson rushes for 137 yards and a touchdown in No. 6 Auburn's 42-14 victory over Louisiana Monroe.
